kpi_info.title: period_duration (period_duration)
kpi_info.use: Duration of the measurement period in minutes.

kpi_info.title: SIGN_RB_DCH_UL_DATA_VOL (M1023C0)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU data transferred in the signalling radio bearer in the uplink direction during the measurement interval. UPDATED:The counter is updated at 20-second intervals, and when the connection is released or the active set is changed.

kpi_info.title: SIGN_RB_DCH_DL_DATA_VOL (M1023C1)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU data transferred in the signalling radio bearer in the downlink direction during the measurement interval. UPDATED:The counter is updated at 20-second intervals, and when the connection is released or the active set is changed.

kpi_info.title: CS_DCH_UL_DATA_VOL (M1023C2)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU data transferred in the CS Call DCH in the uplink direction during the measurement interval. This counter includes AMR, CS Streaming, and CS Conversational calls. UPDATED:The counter is updated at 20-second intervals, and when the connection is released or the active set is changed.

kpi_info.title: CS_DCH_DL_DATA_VOL (M1023C3)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU data transferred in the CS Call DCH in the downlink direction during the measurement interval. UPDATED:The counter is updated at 20-second intervals, and when the connection is released or the active set is changed.

kpi_info.title: RT_PS_DCH_UL_DATA_VOL (M1023C4)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU data transferred in the RT PS DCH in the uplink direction during the measurement interval. UPDATED:The counter is updated at 20-second intervals, and when the connection is released or the active set is changed.

kpi_info.title: RT_PS_DCH_DL_DATA_VOL (M1023C5)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU data transferred in the RT PS DCH in the downlink direction during the measurement interval. UPDATED:The counter is updated at 20-second intervals, and when the connection is released or the active set is changed.

kpi_info.title: NRT_DCH_UL_DATA_VOL (M1023C6)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU data transferred in the NRT DCH in the uplink direction during the measurement interval, excluding HS-DSCH return channels. UPDATED:The counter is updated at 20-second intervals, and when the connection is released or the active set is changed.

kpi_info.title: NRT_DCH_DL_DATA_VOL (M1023C7)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU data transferred in the NRT DCH in the downlink direction during the measurement interval. UPDATED:The counter is updated at 20-second intervals, and when the connection is released or the active set is changed.

kpi_info.title: HS_DSCH_DATA_VOL (M1023C8)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU data transferred with the HS-DSCH in the downlink direction during the measurement interval. When DC-HSDPA is used, this counter is updated only for the primary HS-DSCH serving cell by a value corresponding to the total data volume transferred using both carriers. UPDATED:The counter is updated at 20-second intervals, and when the connection is released or the active set is changed.

kpi_info.title: NRT_DCH_HSDPA_UL_DATA_VOL (M1023C9)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU data transferred in the NRT DCH in the uplink direction during the measurement interval, including only the HS-DSCH return channels. UPDATED:The counter is updated at 20-second intervals, and when the connection is released or the active set is changed.

kpi_info.title: NRT_EDCH_UL_DATA_VOL (M1023C10)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-es PDU data transferred in the E-DCH in the uplink direction during the measurement interval for non-real-time connections. The MAC-es PDU includes MAC-d PDU data and the 6 bits MAC-es header. When DC-HSUPA is used, this counter measures separately the primary and secondary carrier E-DCH data volume. UPDATED:The counter is updated at 20-second intervals, and when the connection is released or the active set is changed.

kpi_info.title: AMR_UL_DATA (M1023C11)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU AMR data transferred in SRNC in the uplink direction measured during the measurement interval. UPDATED: The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counter is updated for only one cell once per each BTS. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: AMR_DL_DATA (M1023C12)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU AMR data in SRNC in the downlink direction measured during the measurement interval. UPDATED: The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counter is updated for only one cell once per each BTS. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: CS_CONV_UL_DATA (M1023C13)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU CS conversational data in SRNC in the uplink direction measured during the measurement interval. This counter does not include CS Voice calls, but only CS Conversational data calls (UDI). UPDATED:The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counter is updated for only one cell once per each BTS. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: CS_CONV_DL_DATA (M1023C14)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU CS conversational data in SRNC in the downlink direction measured during the measurement interval. This counter does not include CS Voice calls, but only CS Conversational data calls (UDI). UPDATED:The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counter is updated for only one cell once per each BTS. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: CS_STREA_UL_DATA (M1023C15)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU CS streaming data in SRNC in the uplink direction measured during the measurement interval. UPDATED: The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counter is updated for only one cell once per each BTS. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: CS_STREA_DL_DATA (M1023C16)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU CS streaming data in SRNC in the uplink direction measured during the measurement interval. UPDATED: The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counter is updated for only one cell once per each BTS. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: PS_STREA_UL_DATA (M1023C17)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU PS streaming data in SRNC in the uplink direction measured during the measurement interval. This counter includes pure Rel99 DCH connections, HS-DSCH uplink return channel and E-DCH. UPDATED: The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counter is updated for only one cell once per each BTS. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: PS_STREA_DL_DATA (M1023C18)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU PS streaming data in SRNC in the downlink direction measured during the measurement interval. This counter includes both Rel99 DCH and HS-DSCH. UPDATED: The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counter is updated for only one cell once per each BTS. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: INTERA_UL_DATA (M1023C19)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU Interactive data in SRNC in uplink direction measured during the measurement interval. This counter includes pure Rel99 DCH connections, HS-DSCH uplink return channel and E-DCH. UPDATED: The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counter is updated for only one cell once per each BTS. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: INTERA_DL_DATA (M1023C20)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU Interactive data in SRNC in downlink direction measured during the measurement interval. This counter includes both Rel99 DCH and HS-DSCH. UPDATED: The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counter is updated for only one cell once per each BTS. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: BGR_UL_DATA (M1023C21)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU Background data in SRNC in uplink direction measured during the measurement interval. This counter includes pure Rel99 DCH connections, HS-DSCH uplink return channel and E-DCH. UPDATED: The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counter is updated for only one cell once per each BTS. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: BGR_DL_DATA (M1023C22)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU background data in SRNC in downlink direction measured during the measurement interval. This counter includes both Rel99 DCH and HS-DSCH. UPDATED: The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counter is updated for only one cell once per each BTS. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: RT_E_DCH_UL_STREA_DATA (M1023C23)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-es PDU Streaming call data for RT E-DCH UL. UPDATED:The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counters are updated for only one cell once per each BTS. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: RT_DCH_HSDPA_UL_STREA_DATA (M1023C24)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU Streaming data for HSDPA UL return channel DCH. UPDATED: The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counters are updated for only one cell once per each BTS. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: RT_HS_DSCH_DL_STREA_DATA (M1023C25)
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU Streaming data for RT HS-DSCH DL. UPDATED: The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counters are updated for only one cell once per each BTS. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: AMR_HS_DSCH_DATA_VOL (M1023C26)
kpi_info.use: The amount of HS-DSCH MAC-d PDU CS Voice data sent to Iub in SRNC. UPDATED:The counter is updated with 20 second intervals, and when the connection is released or the active set is changed.

kpi_info.title: AMR_EDCH_DATA_VOL (M1023C27)
kpi_info.use: The amount of E-DCH MAC-d PDU CS Voice data received from Iub in SRNC. UPDATED:The counter is updated with 20 second intervals, and when the connection is released or the active set is changed.

kpi_info.title: period_duration_sum (period_duration_sum)
kpi_info.use: Duration of the measurement period in minutes.
